(40624, 126518, 3786, 10, 'Like someone in love (cover)', '', '2011-11-21 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 15, '歌詞\r\n\r\nThis change i feel puzzles me\r\n這個改變讓我迷惘不已\r\nit''s strange the real mystery.\r\n感到異常而神祕\r\nmaybe you see it, if you do see it,\r\n也許你看見了,如果你真的看見了\r\nWhat else can it be?\r\n那還會是什麼呢？\r\n\r\nLately I find myself out staring at stars\r\n最近發現自己總凝望著星空\r\nPlaying guitars like someone in love\r\n就像戀愛中的人一樣彈著吉他\r\nSometimes the things I do astound me\r\n有時甚至為自己的行為舉止感到震驚\r\nMostly whenever you''re around me\r\n尤其是當你在我身旁的時候\r\n\r\nLately I seem to walk as though I have wings\r\n最近走起路來像擁有翅膀般的輕盈\r\nBump into things Like someone in love\r\n像戀愛中的人一般魂不守舍\r\nEach time i look at you I''m limp as a glove,\r\n當我看見你時,總像戴著手套那般笨拙\r\nFeeling Like someone in love\r\n就像戀愛中的人一樣\r\n\r\nLately I find myself Out gazing at stars,\r\n最近發現自己總凝望著星空\r\nI play my guitar but I still staring at everything else\r\n我彈著吉他但仍然注視著其他事物\r\nIt''s strange I feel this really puzzles me\r\n這個奇怪的感覺讓我迷惘不已\r\n(You know why?)\r\n你知道嗎\r\nMostly whenever you''re around me\r\n尤其是當你在我身旁的時候\r\n\r\n', '', 271, '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2011-11-21 14:36:03', '2015-03-12 13:49:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
